WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:04.633
What’s wrong with these servants?

2
00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:06.266
Such a major incident has happened to the Emperor,

3
00:00:06.266 --> 00:00:07.766
and you don’t come to console me?

4
00:00:07.766 --> 00:00:09.066
What use is the General Concubine?

5
00:00:09.066 --> 00:00:10.666
Your Majesty, it’s already late at night.

6
00:00:10.666 --> 00:00:12.133
They didn’t dare disturb you.

7
00:00:12.133 --> 00:00:13.666
Let me come and check first.

8
00:00:13.666 --> 00:00:16.366
Hmph, if anything happens to the Emperor,

9
00:00:16.366 --> 00:00:18.666
all of you will lose your heads.

10
00:00:18.666 --> 00:00:20.366
Hahaha.

11
00:00:31.300 --> 00:00:32.633
You should go back.

12
00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:34.366
I’m enough here.

13
00:00:34.366 --> 00:00:35.466
I’m not tired.

14
00:00:36.066 --> 00:00:37.766
I can stay with the Empress Dowager.

15
00:00:37.900 --> 00:00:39.966
Don’t you understand what I’m saying?

16
00:00:41.366 --> 00:00:43.533
You’ve been tired all day too.

17
00:00:43.533 --> 00:00:45.133
It’s best if you go back and rest.

18
00:00:45.133 --> 00:00:48.033
I’ll be here to keep a close watch.

19
00:00:48.166 --> 00:00:49.766
Rest assured.

20
00:00:49.900 --> 00:00:51.966
Then I’ll take my leave.

21
00:00:56.300 --> 00:00:57.400
Please come down.

22
00:01:16.333 --> 00:01:17.466
What’s going on?

23
00:01:17.533 --> 00:01:18.533
The Empress Dowager.

24
00:01:18.533 --> 00:01:21.300
The Emperor is currently in a closed state,

25
00:01:21.300 --> 00:01:22.266
refusing to take medicine.

26
00:01:22.266 --> 00:01:23.666
Tell me the truth.

27
00:01:23.666 --> 00:01:26.166
Why did the Emperor suddenly fall ill?

28
00:01:26.600 --> 00:01:30.266
Empress Dowager, the Emperor has been overthinking,

29
00:01:30.266 --> 00:01:31.400
and has overworked himself,

30
00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:33.933
plus he has a toxin in his body,

31
00:01:33.933 --> 00:01:35.133
and has caught a cold.

32
00:01:35.133 --> 00:01:37.700
His body is also overwhelmed.

33
00:01:37.700 --> 00:01:39.000
Is there any way

34
00:01:39.500 --> 00:01:41.433
to make the Emperor willing to take medicine?

35
00:01:41.466 --> 00:01:42.700
I think

36
00:01:42.933 --> 00:01:46.066
when Concubine Rong fed the Emperor medicine before,

37
00:01:46.066 --> 00:01:47.500
such a situation didn’t occur.

38
00:01:47.500 --> 00:01:49.300
It shows that the Emperor

39
00:01:49.300 --> 00:01:51.100
is willing to be close to Concubine Rong.

40
00:01:51.100 --> 00:01:53.866
Perhaps Concubine Rong should carefully take care of him.

41
00:01:53.866 --> 00:01:56.433
This would benefit the Emperor’s recovery.

42
00:01:57.066 --> 00:01:58.100
It’s Concubine Rong again.

43
00:01:58.700 --> 00:02:01.800
Go and bring Concubine Rong to me.
